data.description: Cute and cozy 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom, 2 attached carport with a guest house. Main house approx. 1064 sf and the guest house approx. 591 sf. Main house updates in 2023 – vinyl plank flooring, repainted inside, and blinds. Main house bathroom updates in 2023 - toilet, tile, fixtures, sink and mirror. Main house with screened-patio / breezeway. Guest house on slab foundation: 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom and storage building. Kitchen with granite counter tops. Guest house updates in 2021 - hot water heater, garbage disposal, microwave, repainted inside, 2 ceiling fans, and 2 window units. Kitchen window unit heats and cools. Bedroom window unit only cools.  Property located on a corner lot. 1 attached garage was converted into a workshop. Backyard fenced with inground pool. The property is conveniently located to schools, shopping, and major traffic arteries. Check out the photos! Call or text for more details.
